{"tid":1919550,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"［恨死隔離］特朗普救市:薪俸稅今年內降至零","createTime":"2020-03-11T00:35:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-11T00:40:14.000Z","uid":48083,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4ad78d6beaa68245b9b5f257a54b141ad6690b9c","tid":1919550,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T00:35:13.000Z","msg":"【信報財經新聞】美國總統特朗普推動經濟刺激措施，冀紓緩疫情對經濟造成的負面影響。據白宮官員透露，響頭炮的救市政策包括今年其餘時間內，將薪俸稅稅率降低至零。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普周二到國會山莊，與共和黨議員商討經濟刺激措施。有白宮官員向CNBC透露，特朗普向國會議員提出，將薪俸稅稅率降低至零，減稅期限維持至今年之內。<br />\n<br />\n擬扶持頁岩油開採商<br />\n<br />\n不過，國會對特朗普的減稅方案持懷疑態度。<br />\n<br />\n另外，特朗普據稱將資助美國頁岩油行業。沙地阿拉伯與俄羅斯近日爆發石油減價戰，導致油價急速滑落，美國頁岩油開採商深受其苦，有分析認為，部分油商或陷入破產邊緣。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://finance.now.com/mobile/news/article/570944\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffinance.now.com%2Fmobile%2Fnews%2Farticle%2F570944&d=Pl33APIo1S6IjQ3qGLZsPebr9%2BGymSeLOXabm6KdyvY%3D&h=f2388a1d\" target=\"_blank\">https://finance.now.com/mobile/news/article/570944</a>"},{"pid":"a3c6070d30fd9ba1fca855f27bf76c387353ad28","tid":1919550,"uid":4942,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T00:35:54.000Z","msg":"drop to zero <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"058fe82f4cf88485abbc3ad581a40a28713802fd","tid":1919550,"uid":22590,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T00:40:14.000Z","msg":"安倍可否跟風將10%消售稅降至零? THX"}]}